{"title":"差最小","time_limit":1000,"memory_limit":128,"tags":["DP"],"operation":{"submit":"https://syzoj.com/problem/24#submit_code","submissions":"https://syzoj.com/submissions?problem_id=24","statistics":"https://syzoj.com/problem/24/statistics/fastest","testdata":"https://syzoj.com/problem/24/testdata","discussion":"https://syzoj.com/discussion/problem/24"},"statement":[{"title":"题目描述","type":"description","format":"markdown","require":["katex"],"content":"现在有 $n$ 个整数，要你从里面选出 $c$ 个数字，按顺序组成新的序列，这个序列的花费定义为相邻元素的差的绝对值的和。\r\n\r\n现在请你找出里面花费最小的序列。"},{"title":"输入格式","type":"input_format","format":"markdown","require":["katex"],"content":"第一行两个整数 $n$ 和 $c$\r\n\r\n第二行n个数字"},{"title":"输出格式","type":"output_format","format":"markdown","require":["katex"],"content":"一行一个整数，表示花费最小序列。"},{"title":"样例","type":"example","format":"markdown","require":["katex"],"content":"#### 样例输入\r\n```\r\n5 3\r\n3 6 8 2 5\r\n```\r\n#### 样例输出\r\n```\r\n4\r\n```\r\n#### 样例解释\r\n其中 $3,2,5$ 组成的序列的花费为 $|3-2|+|2-5|=4 $，不存在比这个花费更小的序列"},{"title":"数据范围与提示","type":"limit_and_hint","format":"markdown","require":["katex"],"content":"$1 \\le n,c \\le 300$"}]}